msgstr "Прив'язка доменного імені до бази даних Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:339
msgid ""
"Ensure you have :ref:`added a CNAME record <domain-name/cname>` to your "
"domain name's DNS **before** mapping your domain name to your Odoo database."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:342
